==hound== (as verb) to relentlessly pursue or pester someone
==specimen== an individual animal, plant, or piece of a substance used as an example of its species or type for scientific study or display
==fuss== a display of unnecessary or excessive excitement, activity, or concern about something; to show excessive concern or activity about something
==shuttle== a form of transport that travels regularly between two places; to move or travel frequently between two places
==pail== a bucket
==shove== to push (someone or something) roughly
